get_sql: SELECT train.row_id, i1.webp as webp_input, i2.webp as webp_expected, i1.width as input_width, i1.height as input_height, i2.width as expected_width, i2.height as expected_height FROM train, images i1, images i2 WHERE train.input = i1.row_id AND train.expected = i2.row_id AND train.row_id - ?1 < 32 AND train.row_id - ?1 >= 0
len_sql: SELECT COUNT(*) as len FROM train
